 around 1100 students.\n\n==PSAA Departments==\n\n*Flight crew ground training\n*Flight safety training\n*Crew Skills Development (CSD)\n*Aviation support services training\n* Technical services\n*Flight operations performance engineering\n*Flight operations manuals & publications\n*Flight crew training plans\n*Basic flight training\n\n==See also==\n*[[Saudi Arabian Airlines]]\n*[[List of universities in Saudi Arabia]]\n\n== External links ==\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20060703150509/http://fo.sv.net/psaa/Default.asp  Official Website]\n\n{{coord missing|Saudi Arabia}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Prince Sultan Aviation Academy}}\n[[Category:2004 establishments in Saudi Arabia]]\n[[Category:Educational institutions established in 2004]]\n[[Category:Universities and colleges in Saudi Arabia]]\n[[Category:Education in Jeddah]]\n[[Category:Saudia]]\n[[Category:Aviation schools]]\n", "text_old": "{{multiple issues|\n{{Unreferenced|date=August 2010}}\n{{Notability|Organizations|date=August 2010}}\n}}\n\n{{Infobox university\n| name              = Prince Sultan Aviation Academy\n| native_name       = \n| image_name        = Saudi Arabian Airlines logo.png\n| image_size        = \n| image_alt         = \n| caption           = [[Saudi Arabian Airlines]] logo\n| latin_name        = \n| motto             = \n| motto_lang        = \n| mottoeng          = \n| established       = 2004\n| closed            = \n| type              = \n| affiliation       = \n| endowment         = \n| budget            = \n| officer_in_charge = \n| chairman          = \n| chancellor        = \n| president         = \n| vice-president    = \n| superintendent    = \n| provost           = \n| vice_chancellor   = \n| rector            = \n| principal         = \n| dean              = Eng. Khalid A. Al-Molhem\n| director          = \n| head_label        = \n| head              = \n| academic_staff    = \n| administrative_staff  = \n| students          = 6700\n| undergrad         = \n| 