{"title_page": "Abdul Ghani Kasuba", "text_new": "{{BLP sources|date=August 2017}}\n{{Infobox officeholder\n|honorific-prefix   = \n|name               = Abdul Ghani Kasuba\n|colorcode          = <!-- HTML color code (e.g. red, #FF0000 or affiliated Party metadata color template) or transparent for no coloring -->\n|image              = Gubernur Maluku Utara Abdul Gani Kasuba.jpg\n|imagesize          =\n|smallimage         = <!--If this is specified, \"image\" should not be.-->\n|alt                =\n|caption            =\n|order              =\n|office             = Governor of [[North Maluku]]\n|term_start       = 5 May 2014\n|term_end         = \n|vicepresident      =\n|deputy             = Muhammad Natsir Thaib\n|lieutenant         =\n|president        = [[Susilo Bambang Yudhoyono]]<br>[[Joko Widodo]]\n|succeeding        =\n|predecessor       = Tanribali Lamo\n|successor         = \n|constituency       =\n|majority           =\n|order2             =  <!--Can be repeated up to eight times by changing the number-->\n|deputy2            =  <!--Can be repeated up to eight times by changing the number-->\n|lieutenant2        =  <!--Can be repeated up to eight times by changing the number-->\n|birth_date         = 21 December 1951\n|birth_place        = [[Bacan Islands]], [[South Halmahera Regency]], North Maluku, [[Indonesia]]\n|death_date         = \n|death_place        =\n|restingplace       =\n|restingplacecoordinates =\n|birthname          =\n|citizenship        = Indonesian\n|nationality        =\n|party              = [[Prosperous Justice Party]]\n|otherparty         =  <!--For additional political affiliations-->\n|spouse             = Faoniah Hi Djaohar\n|relations          =\n|children           = Muhammad Thariq Kasuba<br>Nazlatan Ukhra Kasuba<br>Aminatuz Zahrah Kasuba<br>Nurul Izzah Kasuba\n|residence          =\n|alma_mater         = [[Islamic University of Madinah]]\n|occupation         = Politician\n|profession         =\n|cabinet            =\n|commit